@NODE History "History"
@{u}History@{uu}

V1.0 - The first version!

V1.1 - Forgot the DirScanner.listing file, included now :).

       Updated the guide and a few files.
       
       Updated the keyfile reader and some other bits in the main program.

V1.2 - Fixed a few bugs.

       Aminet directories are now obtained from the info/adt/tree file,
       although replacement directory descriptions can be put in the
       DirScanner.listing (ie. if they are too long!)
       
       If descriptions are too long, they get shortened automatically (with ..
       at the end).
       
       Put in a few presumed (easier) things for Aminet CDs.
       
V1.3 - Changed & fixed a few things.

       Changed the guide a little.

       Now handles CDs with spaces in the device name correctly :o).
       
       Not much else, nobody sent me any new structures or anything, please
       please send me details so I can support different CD structures in
       future versions.
       
V1.4 - Re-wrote path checking thingy and lots of other things to do with paths,
       should be OK with sub directories and stuff other than CD0-CD9.
       
       Added function to remove .info, .readme, .nfo etc. whenever possible.
       
       Added function to remove empty or problematic directories from listings.
       
       A few bug fixes & other small changes such as text.
       
       Added timer so you can see how fast (slow!) DirScanner is :o).
       
       Fixed a few problems using the unknown or create index CD functions.
       
       Supports Other-reg keyfiles.
       
@ENDNODE

